title: Warhammer 40,000 Dawn of War Soulstorm (El Capitan)
description:
...the grim nightmare of the far future, where there is only war and the galaxy's alight and everyone's got a headache...

Play as one of either 9 races in a war for domination set in the Warhammer 40k Universe. 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Notes: 

1. This is a WineSkin Port. I am not a porting professional so do not expect this to be a perfect port. There may be some bugs but the game is, overall, playable.

2. This is a reupload of a port I made a couple of years back. This now works with the latest version of OS X El Capitan.

3. I haven't finished testing this yet as I was too busy to finish the Chaos campaign but so far everything works great and I have yet to experience a game-breaking bug.

4. Enjoy!
